trends: There have been 40 other sightings in Melbourne
There was one other sighting in Melbourne on or around January 24th 2012
Summary: It was moving south to north, at a steady speed, for it's apparent distance it was very large
divs: Sighting DetailsMe my dad and my brother were on our way home fro Plastering when my brother shifted my attention Towards an old building old the side of the road as I looked I noticed a very large white sphere at least 5 miles away moving at a consistent speed and I said it can't be a meteorite (as it left no trail at all and was moving fairly slow) and it could not be a satellite (due to the size of the object) we watched it head north for a good one minute but as the traffic started to move again we lost sight of it.
